# Source Code Structure

This folder contains the core implementation of the volatility forecasting pipeline.

## Modules

- `data_loader.py`  
  Data loading and preprocessing (price data, log returns, scaling)

- `garch_models.py`  
  GARCH-family model estimation (GARCH, EGARCH, GJR-GARCH)

- `forecast_evaluation.py`  
  Out-of-sample forecast evaluation using MSE, MAE, and QLIKE

- `var_backtesting.py`  
  VaR estimation and backtesting (violation rates and Kupiec test)

- `main.py`  
  Main pipeline that integrates all modules and generates results

## Workflow

The pipeline follows:

Data → Volatility Modeling → Forecast Evaluation → VaR Backtesting → Results Export
